<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Photo Project</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2563eb;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 28px;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .welcome-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #1d4ed8);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .feature {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .feature-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #2563eb;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #1d4ed8;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .role-badge {
            background-color: #dbeafe;
            color: #1e40af;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">üì∏ Photo Project</div>
            <h1 class="title">Welcome to Photo Project!</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>
            
            <p>Congratulations! Your email has been successfully verified and your account is now active.</p>

            <div class="welcome-box">
                <h2>üéâ Account Created Successfully!</h2>
                <p>You're now registered as a <span class="role-badge"><%= role %></span></p>
                <p>Your account is ready to use. Start exploring all the amazing features we have to offer!</p>
            </div>

            <div class="features">
                <div class="feature">
                    <div class="feature-icon">üì∏</div>
                    <div class="feature-title">Project Management</div>
                    <p>Create and manage photography projects with ease. Organize your work and collaborate with clients.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature">
                    <div class="feature-icon">üñºÔ∏è</div>
                    <div class="feature-title">Photo Albums</div>
                    <p>Organize your photos into beautiful albums. Share collections with clients and manage access permissions.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature">
                    <div class="feature-icon">üë•</div>
                    <div class="feature-title">Collaboration</div>
                    <p>Work together with team members and clients. Share projects and manage permissions seamlessly.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature">
                    <div class="feature-icon">üîí</div>
                    <div class="feature-title">Secure Storage</div>
                    <p>Your photos are stored securely in the cloud with enterprise-grade security and backup.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="<%= appUrl %>" class="button">Get Started Now</a>
            </div>

            <p>If you have any questions or need help getting started, our support team is here to help!</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>¬© 2024 Photo Project. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>This email was sent to <%= email %>. If you have any questions, please contact our support team.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</body>
</html>


